d and benefited immensely from the course, as the course design is meticulously well planned.',1675577110,1675577110,'course',9,1),(20,5,4,'I really enjoyed this course! I found it really interesting and found that It was very easy to listen to and made me want to listen to it.',1675577270,1675577270,'course',13,1),(21,5,5,'I didn\'t actually believe that learning python would be so easy. Its so simple and I hope YOU will also find this course helpful.',1675577334,1675577334,'course',17,1),(22,5,3,'The course was excellent and its content was more than excellent and I benefited a lot from it. I ask the trainer for more other courses.',1675577370,1675577370,'course',16,1),(23,5,4,'I really enjoyed this course and the course content is well-structured. Thanks to the instructor, I am now able to contribute to product management in my current job by applying the knowledge to certain situations. I have greatly benefited from this course. Superb!',1675577421,1675577421,'course',12,1),(24,2,4,'Clear and conscience course! ',1675804381,1675804381,'course',4,1);
